text: Hugo Koivuniemi (28 December 1894 - 25 May 1963) was a Finnish diver. He competed in the men's plain high diving event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1894 births Category:1963 deaths Category:Finnish male divers Category:Olympic divers of Finland Category:Divers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Vyborg
